description: Over a decade after Terminal, the residents of San Francisco are living a peaceful and prosperous existence thanks to the Program. Every resident is hand-selected and implanted with the chip called Secura. This chip removes the human capacity for violence to maintain the greater good. Only the city's security forces are allowed a brief reprieve from Secura with the help of the drug Freestone in order to do their jobs.Only now there are rumors of Freestone getting out into the open market and it can threaten to upset the delicate balance keeping humanity from extinction.

Worlds are colliding with dueling escape plans and murder plots. This type of converge in a house of cards and its about to come tumbling down. Combine a desperate starlet, a greedy mobster, a hired killer and a delusional Dexter fan all of them stand on the brink but the bigger question is who will pass the point of no return?
name: Point Of No Return

description: With Daken's healing factor destroyed by the effects of the HEAT drug his body is trying to overcome a bullet in his brain. Even if he recovers how does this affect his mind? Guest stars Moon Knight and Donna Kiel work together to discover the identity of the claws killer but it may be Daken all along.
name: Moonwalk, Pt. 3

description:
Few women in all the Seven Kingdoms can match the beauty of Delcardes but Kull is more interested in her traveling companion Saremes, which is her cat. It has been rumored that Saremes is of the old race and Kull wants to hear her counsel. The Hate Witch is dead but the serpent cult are rallying under a powerful wizard. In order to protect the people of Valusia, Kull must unravel the mysteries of this wise and ancient creature.

description: The dark man's empire is crumbling. A spy has slipped through the cracks and his right-hand man has gone rogue. Now his bride is what exactly? It's Nadine's final reckoning with good old Randy Flagg. Things are bad in Vegas and they're about to get worse for our quartet of reluctant heroes as they enter the west. They started with four but there will only be three.

volume.name: The Stand: The Night Has Come

description: A group of ten strangers wake up in a mysterious town with no memory of who they are and how they got there. They are the lone survivors of an apocalyptic event and have been chosen to repopulate the Earth. The bigger question is what is the true nature of their fate?
name: untitled
